Knowledge Check 5.5
Given the following vector, "X=c(2,4,4,4,5,5,7,9)", what is the Mean, Median and Standard Deviation? Please select the correct answer.
a. Mean=5, Median=4.5, Standard Deviation=2.1
b. Mean=4, Median=4.5, Standard Deviation=1.5
c. Mean=5, Median=5, Standard Deviation=2.1
d. Mean=4, Median=4.5, Standard Deviation=1.5 

NOTE: checked in R Studio:

> x=c(2,4,4,4,5,5,7,9)
> x
[1] 2 4 4 4 5 5 7 9
> mean(x)
[1] 5
> median(x)
[1] 4.5
> sd(x, na.rm = FALSE)
[1] 2.13809
> 


